title: 1915-A
statement: A. Odd One Outtime limit per test1 secondmemory limit per test256 megabytesinputstandard inputoutputstandard outputYou are given three digits $$$a$$$, $$$b$$$, $$$c$$$. You are given three digits $a$, $b$, and $c$. Two of the digits are the same, and the third digit is different. Find the digit that appears only once. 

Input:
